{"id": "ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 753, "displayName": {"text": "Proof Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Compact cafe & bakery offering fresh-made pastries, sandwiches, cakes & locally roasted coffee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FeE16ZENUR3MzZEZVNVNGZDVPVVpwVldWaVRHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’m so happy I finally got to try the famous sea salt chocolate chip cookie from Proof!! 🍪 It was absolutely deeeeelicious and not too sweet. I didn’t like the hojicha strawberry combo for the mochi cake — strawberry tasted strange, so next time would try a different dessert. Super looking forward to trying the croissant for breakfast!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’m so happy I finally got to try the famous sea salt chocolate chip cookie from Proof!! 🍪 It was absolutely deeeeelicious and not too sweet. I didn’t like the hojicha strawberry combo for the mochi cake — strawberry tasted strange, so next time would try a different dessert. Super looking forward to trying the croissant for breakfast!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Wesley Erickson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110387233885894646736/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBOY_t0CKbKimeOCJcDaTmkxIzSVdHgS8Dn_MZ0PmAs0cPlg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-28T07:31:12.318594641Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FeE16ZENUR3MzZEZVNVNGZDVPVVpwVldWaVRHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FeE16ZENUR3MzZEZVNVNGZDVPVVpwVldWaVRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c0dafedef551:0xb9cfa4606ad3ed85"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taS2EzWlZka3haWm01UlRHOW5hSFoyYmpoMlZVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This bakery is exceptional. Went on a Saturday late morning and found a small line outside but it moved fast and wasn't a long wait. Unassuming location, you can't assume by the exterior or small interior the quality and flavor. We tried the focaccia, bread, croissants, cookies, caramel cornbread cake, tart and pie, and all were delicious. High quality, well made, not too sweet, unique flavors. Definitely worth a trip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This bakery is exceptional. Went on a Saturday late morning and found a small line outside but it moved fast and wasn't a long wait. Unassuming location, you can't assume by the exterior or small interior the quality and flavor. We tried the focaccia, bread, croissants, cookies, caramel cornbread cake, tart and pie, and all were delicious. High quality, well made, not too sweet, unique flavors. Definitely worth a trip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alfred K", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109101913736582816979/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7vK0uvvbZtkuXS5T-7j2dqt9-egJwqPOk1DOvIL4OUt_WinA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T15:33:24.551948271Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taS2EzWlZka3haWm01UlRHOW5hSFoyYmpoMlZVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taS2EzWlZka3haWm01UlRHOW5hSFoyYmpoMlZVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c0dafedef551:0xb9cfa4606ad3ed85"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZd2RtTnpNRnB4ZFVOalEzbDNVRmt5WTB4ZmNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Came in expecting to grab breakfast because this establishment is listed as a vegan-friendly bakery. Unfortunately, there were zero vegan options available when I visited, which meant there was nothing I could purchase or eat.\n\nIf you’re going to advertise your business as vegan-friendly, there should be at least a few vegan options available on the menu. Sadly, this experience was disappointing, and I won’t be able to recommend it based on today’s visit.\n\nHopefully next time they’ll have actual vegan options available for those of us who rely on businesses being accurately represented.\n\n⭐☆☆☆☆ (1 star) because the bakery was open, but no vegan options were available.\n\n– The Traveling Truck Show 🚛✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came in expecting to grab breakfast because this establishment is listed as a vegan-friendly bakery. Unfortunately, there were zero vegan options available when I visited, which meant there was nothing I could purchase or eat.\n\nIf you’re going to advertise your business as vegan-friendly, there should be at least a few vegan options available on the menu. Sadly, this experience was disappointing, and I won’t be able to recommend it based on today’s visit.\n\nHopefully next time they’ll have actual vegan options available for those of us who rely on businesses being accurately represented.\n\n⭐☆☆☆☆ (1 star) because the bakery was open, but no vegan options were available.\n\n– The Traveling Truck Show 🚛✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "KM FM", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107908039980589025745/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYxkMZGlr0NtWXwZ5irzpryWq5cAaG_Rb2I3IrQAndV64WvyNr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-19T16:03:00.098778468Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZd2RtTnpNRnB4ZFVOalEzbDNVRmt5WTB4ZmNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tZd2RtTnpNRnB4ZFVOalEzbDNVRmt5WTB4ZmNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c0dafedef551:0xb9cfa4606ad3ed85"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ZlMxZEpTMDVaVjFwb1VFd3hZVkIwU1hONFlYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Wonderful choices. The kale quiche probably the best quiche I’ve had in my life. Atmosphere and amenities are amazing. Parking is a fight, but it’s LA lol.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Wonderful choices. The kale quiche probably the best quiche I’ve had in my life. Atmosphere and amenities are amazing. Parking is a fight, but it’s LA lol.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Frank Bosch", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108609602477206505597/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuV_YxZA0FUP8EnhgHSIM_FK2eokbrKpvYE7kQlWhaNPG7CM7i=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T22:20:34.593973685Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ZlMxZEpTMDVaVjFwb1VFd3hZVkIwU1hONFlYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4ZlMxZEpTMDVaVjFwb1VFd3hZVkIwU1hONFlYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c0dafedef551:0xb9cfa4606ad3ed85"}, {"name": "places/ChIJUfXe_trAwoARhe3TamCkz7k/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paYWFucHZTM2N0TTJGRU56SnNMVVl4V2pSNFFtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Do NOT and I repeat Do NOT…. Be discouraged by the line 😏. The service is super fast, staff is friendly and the pastries and sandwiches (after 1130) are amazing! I has to hojicha today and it is perfectly sweetened, the salami sandwich is my favorite. We showed up at 9 before heading to the observatory had croissants and then went back for sammies after 🥰.", "languageCode": "en"}, "origi